I'm so despondent.

16:15.055 --> 16:18.100
Cheer up, Homer.
It's only rock-and-roll camp.

16:18.184 --> 16:19.643
But I like it.

16:19.727 --> 16:21.562
[ Sobbing ]

16:24.064 --> 16:27.026
Tell you what. We're doing a
benefit gig before we leave town.

16:27.109 --> 16:29.111
How would you like
to join us on stage?

16:29.195 --> 16:30.196
[ Sniffles ]

16:30.279 --> 16:32.698
- For serious?
- For serious, Homer.

16:32.781 --> 16:34.575
Can I have 4O guest passes?

16:37.411 --> 16:38.412
Whoo-hoo!

16:40.956 --> 16:43.083
Wow. “All access.”

16:43.167 --> 16:46.921
All access.
[ Drooling ]

16:47.004 --> 16:49.131
Good thing it's laminated.
[Laughs]

16:49.924 --> 16:50.925
[Grunts]

16:51.008 --> 16:52.510
Sir, you can't-

16:52.593 --> 16:54.386
All access!
Sorry.

16:54.470 --> 16:57.306
[Gulping]

16:57.389 --> 16:59.308
♪♪ [Humming]

17:00.184 --> 17:01.852
[Women Screaming ]

17:01.936 --> 17:03.479
[ Homer] All access.
[Women Oohing ]

