19:55.359 --> 19:56.944
No!

19:57.027 --> 19:59.488
[All Screaming]

19:59.571 --> 20:01.115
[All Gasping ]

20:08.288 --> 20:11.667
Did you know it was gonna turn
into a riot, Dad? Oh, yeah.

20:11.750 --> 20:15.087
When y0u've been in as many as I
